  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You inhale and take a charging stance, manifesting ripples of fire release chakra throughout your entire body. You coat your body in a flames and dash forward unleashing a devastating kick. Make a melee taijutsu attack against the creature dealing unarmed damage + 4d8 fire damage on a hit. Regardless if you hit or miss, you end your movement within 5 feet of the original target.</p><p>Until the end of your turn, you can target one affected creature with a Taijutsu <em><strong>Finisher</strong></em> regardless of range, <br />once per turn, using either an Action or Bonus action, ignoring its listed casting time.</p>",
